	<p>To request access to or rectification, portability, or erasure of your personal data, or to delete your account, contact Voice Caddie by email at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:contact@voicecaddie.com">contact@voicecaddie.com</a>. Once request is received and processed, user’s account and personally identifiable information will be deleted.</p>
